{"tid":2250100,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"晨早巴士路線建議：26P","createTime":"2020-10-20T01:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T02:18:12.000Z","uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d096f1747185d17dfba3549684ab1904af34e36","tid":2250100,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"利申非巴膠，只係一個頂唔順日日塞車既打工仔<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n- 避開平日早上漆咸道南萬里車龍，縮短車程<br />\n- 為過海乘客提供係紅磡站轉隧巴（有轉乘優惠）<br />\n- 拯救遲起身打工仔<br />\n<br />\n特色：<br />\n行紅磡道上紅磡站，唔行漆咸道南<br />\n<br />\n路線：<br />\n順天至土瓜灣街市同26號一樣<br />\n之後左轉入浙江街再右轉入下路（土瓜灣道）<br />\n停多個「鴻福街」站就爆seed<br />\n左轉入庇利街<br />\n再右轉紅磡道<br />\n直達「紅磡站」<br />\n之後「香港科學館」、「麼地道」、「永安廣場」<br />\n尾站就係「尖沙咀東」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間表：<br />\n最理想係漆咸道南一塞到爆就開<br />\n但冇咁dynamic所以平日開住六班先：<br />\n平日<br />\n07:45<br />\n08:00<br />\n08:15<br />\n08:30<br />\n08:45<br />\n09:00<br />\n星期六及公眾假期暫停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"2a4ffdcc430fdd1e894673ae1fd4657b894ad9fc","tid":2250100,"uid":139082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:12:49.000Z","msg":"行承啟道爆seed行足全條下路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以做埋啟德果堆客"},{"pid":"e5f94502ad9b1b795435de45282d985cedd3e96f","tid":2250100,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"運輸署：現有服務已能應付乘客需求、可以使用鐵路服務&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"7abbc4dd9b6e9288f0177dfdcdb8bae1690b4e02","tid":2250100,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a4ffdcc430fdd1e894673ae1fd4657b894ad9fc","tid":2250100,"uid":139082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:12:49.000Z","msg":"行承啟道爆seed行足全條下路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以做埋啟德果堆客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"都唔錯wo